1
00:00:27,350 --> 00:00:30,036
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:30,037 --> 00:00:31,986
=Episode 7=
(She only had to stand there,)

3
00:00:31,987 --> 00:00:34,007
(and she became my god.)

4
00:00:56,340 --> 00:00:57,500
Let go!

5
00:01:43,740 --> 00:01:44,700
Xi.

6
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:10,739
Don't run.

7
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:11,700
Zhao.

8
00:02:12,740 --> 00:02:13,780
Coming.

9
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:58,060
Xi.

10
00:02:59,825 --> 00:03:03,224
♪Through countless nights
across rivers and mountains♪

11
00:03:03,225 --> 00:03:06,599
♪Yet we couldn't last through the years♪

12
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:09,739
♪This parting gathers all joy
and sorrow into silence♪

13
00:03:09,740 --> 00:03:10,620
I...

14
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:12,940
I'm here.

15
00:03:14,975 --> 00:03:18,461
♪Through love and life,
I roamed the mortal world♪

16
00:03:18,462 --> 00:03:24,600
♪Only after a fleeting century
did I learn how shallow this love was♪

17
00:03:24,637 --> 00:03:27,539
♪You are the snow
that rests on timeless hills♪

18
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:29,199
(Bite marks?)

19
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:32,299
♪Yet mistaken for the moon♪

20
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:34,180
(Could that dream have been real?)

21
00:03:34,187 --> 00:03:38,124
♪travel a thousand miles to you♪

22
00:03:38,125 --> 00:03:40,919
♪You are a night of falling petals♪

23
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:45,199
♪Gone in a blink,
you fade to the horizon♪

24
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:50,907
♪Telling me not to long for you♪
(Qingxin Pavilion)

25
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:03,900
(It was exhausting
blocking the moonlight last night.)

26
00:04:04,580 --> 00:04:07,060
(Master will definitely reward me.)

27
00:04:12,460 --> 00:04:13,940
(Hey cutie,)

28
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:17,380
(if you fall for him again
in this life,)

29
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:19,460
(I won't be able to save you.)

30
00:04:42,587 --> 00:04:43,627
Did I

31
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:46,460
hurt you yesterday?

32
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:51,660
Quite the move you have right there.

33
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:53,660
Biting and grabbing me like that.

34
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:55,420
Does it still hurt?

35
00:05:00,420 --> 00:05:01,540
Of course it hurts.

36
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:19,220
(Baobao,)

37
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:21,980
(go find me a bone worm suitable
for refinement.)

38
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:23,300
(Yes, Master.)

39
00:05:23,980 --> 00:05:24,980
Baobao?

40
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:26,900
She's gone out

41
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,300
and hasn't returned yet.

42
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:29,980
I've got a few minor wounds.

43
00:05:30,780 --> 00:05:32,060
I'll need your help.

44
00:05:43,780 --> 00:05:44,980
It might hurt a little.

45
00:05:45,420 --> 00:05:46,420
Bear with it.

46
00:05:54,660 --> 00:05:56,220
Why is your body so hot?

47
00:05:56,340 --> 00:05:58,740
Is your fever still not gone?

48
00:06:02,660 --> 00:06:04,740
The weather's nice today.

49
00:06:04,780 --> 00:06:05,780
I'll go out...

50
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:07,300
to get some sun.

51
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:22,860
Why did you

52
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:26,100
lose control like a beast last night?

53
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:27,780
Every full moon,

54
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:29,539
I lose my powers

55
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:30,740
and the bite marks appear.

56
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:31,980
So,

57
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:34,860
is the demon root in me

58
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:36,500
related to this?

59
00:06:39,180 --> 00:06:40,459
A hundred years ago,

60
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,740
the demon heart caused

61
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:43,980
corrupt growths to sprout in humans,

62
00:06:44,340 --> 00:06:45,740
feeding on flesh and blood.

63
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,540
When they bloom,

64
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,300
their pollen spreads easily.

65
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:51,980
Before long,

66
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:53,500
those infected

67
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:54,899
would die.

68
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:56,500
Then is there no cure

69
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:58,860
to this illness?

70
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:02,659
Verdant Decay is planted
in humans by the demon heart

71
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:04,180
using its own power.

72
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:05,660
It's extremely hard to cure.

73
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:08,779
There are three methods.

74
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:10,060
What are they?

75
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:11,540
First,

76
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:14,100
consume a god's flesh and blood.

77
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:16,540
It cures the illness,

78
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:19,245
but turns the victim
into a Flower Slave.

79
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:21,060
So those Flower Slaves

80
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:24,339
were once human?

81
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:26,099
After being infected,

82
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:28,780
they devoured you on full moon nights.

83
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:31,740
So,

84
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:34,100
what you suffered last night

85
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:35,740
was because of this?

86
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:39,540
This method is out of the question.
What about the second one?

87
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:42,540
Second,

88
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:45,980
cut out the corrupted part.

89
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:49,420
If it's on the limbs, that's manageable.

90
00:07:49,900 --> 00:07:52,019
But if it's in the head...

91
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:52,900
Enough.

92
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:55,060
What about the third?

93
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,899
The third...

94
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:01,500
I just destroyed her demon heart.

95
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:04,019
She should be dead.

96
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:07,299
If the demon root remains,
the demon heart can't truly die.

97
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:09,300
Find the demon root

98
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:12,220
within your flesh.

99
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:13,420
This way,

100
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:16,300
Verdant Decay will vanish.

101
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:19,779
Other than cutting

102
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:21,419
into my flesh,

103
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:22,900
is there another way to find it?

104
00:08:24,220 --> 00:08:25,779
You don't seem afraid at all.

105
00:08:25,780 --> 00:08:27,459
I need to remove the demon root,

106
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:29,860
but I also need to stay alive.

107
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:32,180
If Verdant Decay returns,

108
00:08:32,660 --> 00:08:33,900
Ning

109
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:36,420
will never know peace.

110
00:08:36,580 --> 00:08:37,740
Don't worry.

111
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:40,660
I've crushed the demon heart.

112
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:43,740
And with that stab you gave her,

113
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:45,100
she won't recover

114
00:08:45,340 --> 00:08:46,660
anytime soon.

115
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:49,579
I've sent Baobao
to find a suitable bone worm.

116
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:51,740
Once I refine it
into a root-seeking worm,

117
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:54,419
it will keep you alive

118
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:55,660
and help locate the demon root.

119
00:08:59,980 --> 00:09:01,100
In that case,

120
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:02,659
since we need each other,

121
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:03,780
that makes us allies.

122
00:09:03,900 --> 00:09:05,779
Allies should be honest.

123
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,980
From now on,

124
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:09,860
you are not to insult or hurt me.

125
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:14,980
From now on,

126
00:09:15,180 --> 00:09:16,220
I'll protect you

127
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:19,700
until we find the demon root.

128
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:25,460
Pinky promise.

129
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:29,740
(Xi,)

130
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:33,380
(were you also possessed
by demon heart in your past life?)

131
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:36,500
(Was it you I loved
or the demon heart?)

132
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:38,220
(And the one who loved me...)

133
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:40,340
(was it you or her?)

134
00:09:42,637 --> 00:09:45,307
(Ning Capital)

135
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:52,820
The Flower Slaves have everyone on edge.

136
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:53,860
Father,

137
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:54,980
look.

138
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,980
his street used to be lively,

139
00:09:57,020 --> 00:09:58,580
but now there's no one.

140
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:00,539
People are too scared to come out.

141
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:01,860
What are you talking about?

142
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:03,820
General.

143
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:05,179
As per your orders,

144
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:07,379
I've conducted a search across the city.

145
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:09,580
All Flower Slaves in the city
have been captured.

146
00:10:09,900 --> 00:10:10,779
Reports concerning them

147
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:12,779
in the city have decreased recently.

148
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:15,580
Things should return to normal soon.

149
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:20,500
Don't let your guard down.
We still don't know how many there are.

150
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:23,020
Increase patrols everywhere.

151
00:10:23,380 --> 00:10:24,659
No mistakes.

152
00:10:24,660 --> 00:10:25,380
Yes, sir.

153
00:10:26,020 --> 00:10:27,460
Thief!

154
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:29,779
Catch the thief!

155
00:10:29,780 --> 00:10:30,699
Continue patrol.

156
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:31,419
Yes, sir!

157
00:10:31,420 --> 00:10:32,580
Get him!

158
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:34,659
Dashing.

159
00:10:34,660 --> 00:10:36,140
He really is.

160
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:37,819
That thief's in trouble though.

161
00:10:37,820 --> 00:10:38,899
if General Pei caught him,

162
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:41,100
he won't walk away
without a few broken ribs.

163
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:43,299
Enough chatter.

164
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:44,100
Let's go.

165
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,500
(It's him.)

166
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:10,380
Stealing in Ning Capital?

167
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:13,899
You're playing with fire.

168
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:15,100
Spare me please, General.

169
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:17,619
Everything I stole is here.

170
00:11:17,620 --> 00:11:19,100
Please forgive me.

171
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,620
Where did this jade pendant come from?

172
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:26,179
I stole it from a woman

173
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:27,700
at Baihua Hall outside the city.

174
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:29,740
(Could Her Highness be there?)

175
00:11:29,820 --> 00:11:30,940
(No time to waste.)

176
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:05,020
Who are you?

177
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:06,980
Who am I?

178
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:08,340
And you think

179
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:11,340
you're worthy of asking?

180
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,709
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

181
00:12:20,710 --> 00:12:23,559
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

182
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:26,299
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

183
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:27,929
♪Let the long shadows♪

184
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:33,530
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

185
00:12:33,580 --> 00:12:35,179
♪If in a dream♪

186
00:12:35,180 --> 00:12:37,939
♪I can hear your voice♪

187
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:40,789
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

188
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:43,389
♪Let it be us♪

189
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:48,179
♪drawing endlessly close♪

190
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:49,939
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

191
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:52,590
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

192
00:12:52,810 --> 00:12:55,529
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

193
00:12:55,530 --> 00:12:57,179
♪Not even in time♪

194
00:12:57,180 --> 00:13:02,839
♪to tell you how I feel♪

195
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,379
♪If the rain won't stop♪

196
00:13:04,380 --> 00:13:07,129
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

197
00:13:07,130 --> 00:13:10,099
♪Let love go on♪

198
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:12,649
♪Until forever♪

199
00:13:12,650 --> 00:13:17,289
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

200
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:19,899
♪Until forever♪

201
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:27,010
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
